sagex.phoenix.scrapers.xbmc

Class XbmcMovieProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • sagex.phoenix.scrapers.xbmc.XbmcMovieProcessor

  • public class XbmcMovieProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
    This tries to emulate the XMBC Process. Much of what is done in this code was learned from looking at the original c++ code http://xbmc.svn.sourceforge.net/ viewvc/xbmc/trunk/XBMC/xbmc/utils/IMDB.cpp?view=markup
